_sText: aim_tropics by "Rusty9k" - Jora Hill is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial-No Derivative Works 3.0 New Zealand License. Aim_tropics by Rusty9k Inspired by piracy! (not the software kind :P) The map is basicaly a small cove surrounded by volcanos!, Its hard to describe this kind of map so take a look at the screenshots. The water looks very nice, as long as you dont go underneath it, there is a glitch where you cant see the water properly if you go under it, very sorry, i cant fix it. There are no other major bugs I can think of, the 3d skybox could use a little work, but I dont have the time! Please contact me at jorahill@hotmail.com if you want to do something with this map like a video or something. Enjoy! - Rusty9k
